[[File:Musrestaurangen_i_Malmö.jpg|right|thumb|The mouse restaurant Il Topolino, December 2016]] [[File:Mustivolit_på_Södra_Förstadsgatan.jpg|thumb|Amusement park in Malmö, April 2017]] '''Anonymouse''' is an anonymous Swedish [[Artist collective|artists collective]], notable for [[street installation]]s in [[Sweden]]. They build [[mouse]]-themed [[miniature art|miniatures]] and display them in public. The first work was the restaurant ''Il Topolino'' that appeared on Bergsgatan in [[Malmö]].<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://time.com/4602411/anonymouse-mice-shops/ |title=These Tiny Shops for Mice on Real Streets Will Blow Your Mind |website=Time |access-date=2017-11-09}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.lonelyplanet.com/news/2016/12/14/tiny-mouse-cafe-shop-sweden/ |title=A tiny mouse café and shop has appeared on a street in Sweden |last=Planet |first=Lonely |website=www.lonelyplanet.com |language=en |access-date=2017-11-09}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.sydsvenskan.se/2016-12-08/vem-ar-musen-som-oppnat-butik-pa-bergsgatan |title=Vem är musen som öppnat butik på Bergsgatan? |work=Sydsvenskan |access-date=2017-11-09 |language=sv-SE}} </ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.expressen.se/kvallsposten/de-ligger-bakom-musrestaurangen/ |title=Skaparna av musrestaurangen: "Rackarns bra tålamod" |work=Expressen |access-date=2017-11-09 |language=sv}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.dn.se/kultur-noje/konst-form/konstinstallation-i-musformat-skapar-uppstandelse-i-malmo/ |title=Konstinstallation i musformat skapar uppståndelse i Malmö - DN.SE |date=2016-12-08 |work=DN.SE |access-date=2017-11-09 |language=sv-se}}</ref> It was vandalized a few weeks later.<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.sydsvenskan.se/2016-12-29/musrestaurangen-pa-bergsgatan-vandaliserad |title=Musrestaurangen på Bergsgatan vandaliserad |work=Sydsvenskan |access-date=2017-11-09 |language=sv-SE |id=2016-12-29}}</ref> In April 2017 they created an amusement park at Södra Förstadsgatan.<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.dn.se/nyheter/sverige/tivoli-for-gnagare-har-oppnat-i-malmo/ |title=Tivoli för gnagare har öppnat i Malmö - DN.SE |date=2017-04-23 |work=DN.SE |access-date=2017-11-09 |language=sv-se}}</ref> In September 2017 two shops and a gas station opened in [[Borås]].<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.thelocal.se/20170907/swedens-anonymouse-street-art-packs-up-from-malm-to-start-afresh-in-bors |title=Sweden's AnonyMouse packs up from Malmö to start afresh in Borås |date=2017-09-07 |language=en |access-date=2017-11-09}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://metro.co.uk/2016/12/10/anonymous-artists-are-creating-tiny-shops-for-mice-around-sweden-6314095/|title=Anonymous artists are creating tiny shops for mice around Sweden|date=2016-12-10|work=Metro|access-date=2017-11-09|language=en-GB}}</ref>
Inspired by Anonymouse, Gothenburg artist Staffan Lindholm built and displayed on the streets of [[Haga, Gothenburg]] a mouse-themed cheese shop, a shoe shop, a motorcycle shop and a gym. <ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.gp.se/nyheter/g%25C3%25B6teborg/gym-f%25C3%25B6r-m%25C3%25B6ss-har-%25C3%25B6ppnat-i-haga-1.7329725 |title=Gym för möss har öppnat i Haga |website=Göteborgs-Posten |language=sv |access-date=2018-07-25}}</ref>
