Machomane{{Pronunciation-needed}} is a type of dance which is popularly known to be performed by [[traditional]] [[healers]] in [[Botswana]] who use strong African traditional medicine. Machomane dance is usually accompanied by three people who are drum beaters.<ref>{{cite web|title=Machomane music|url=http://www.kutlwano.gov.bw/mobile/kut-article-teaser-detail.php?aid=302&cid=5&mid=74|accessdate=21 September 2017}}</ref>

