'''Maikoor''' is an island in the [[Aru Islands]] in the [[Arafura Sea]]. It is situated in the [[Maluku Province]], [[Indonesia]]. Its area is 398&nbsp;km². The other main islands in the archipelago are [[Kobroor]], [[Tanahbesar]] (also called Wokam), [[Trangan]] and [[Kola Island|Kola]].

