The '''Roman Catholic Diocese of Odienné''' ({{lang-la|Odiennen(sis)}}) is a [[diocese]] located in the city of [[Odienné]] in the [[Ecclesiastical province]] of [[Roman Catholic Archdiocese of Korhogo|Korhogo]] in [[Côte d'Ivoire]].
